task.summary: Lite JAVA web framework, first commitment
Add bean container and dependency injection.

1. Add some util classes and abstract types 2. Complete the HelperLoader which deals with the Initialization of the framework 3. Complete the ControllerHelper, it combines the requests and the corresponding handlers
1. Initialize the proxy framework, creating proxyMap and targetMap (mappings between proxy class and target classes, target class and proxies)
